---
title: Retro Burgers with Caramelized Onions and Roasted Sweet Potatoes
description: Caramelized onions, cheddar cheese, toasty buns and perfectly packed patties; this burger comes together quickly and will make your weeknight dinner a delicious event!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/burger-retro-30ab0b09.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ca/recipecards/card/retro-burgers-62a866ac6065111cd80a6a28-80bf4514.pdf
